==Scots==

===Noun===
'''dander'''

#''(Ulster Scots dialect):'' A gentle meandering walk with no particular haste or purpose.  Eg. to go for a dander on the beach. 

===Verb===
'''dander'''

# ''(Ulster Scots dialect)'' To walk along with no particular haste.  eg. to dander along the beach

